room_title: Escape room "The Saloon" by Southern Escape Room in Monroe (LA)
room_description: Gather up your gang, saddle up your horses and meet up at the Longbranch saloon to get your gold but be careful, rumor has it that the loot has been wired with explosives and rigged to blow. So disarm the bomb, grab your gold and ride off into the sunset before your time is up.
